<span id="freeTextContainer18348844523387377187">Wow! I just finished this amazing book today! I devoured it in only 3 days!! I found the other day by chance, when I was taking a look at amazon indie authors contest. Immediately I felt in love with this beautiful book cover. But don&apos;t misunderstand me, in this book, there is beauty everywhere, out of the book and also inside it. The story is so powerful, so uplifting that I still in shock! Miquel Reina please write more books, I want to read more of your creative and touching stories. I suppos</span>
  <span id="freeText18348844523387377187" style="display:none">Wow! I just finished this amazing book today! I devoured it in only 3 days!! I found the other day by chance, when I was taking a look at amazon indie authors contest. Immediately I felt in love with this beautiful book cover. But don't misunderstand me, in this book, there is beauty everywhere, out of the book and also inside it. The story is so powerful, so uplifting that I still in shock! Miquel Reina please write more books, I want to read more of your creative and touching stories. I suppose that I don't have to say more about the book, you only have to read it, especially if you enjoy books as LIFE OF PI, THE ALCHEMIST or ALL THE LIGHT WE CANNOT SEE. Its a masterpiece!</span>
